OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1780938366
OL,3,CFormer care home manager avoids jail
OL,4,Cover sexual abuse at children's home
OL,6,FThe former boss of a children's home
OL,7,Fin Halifax has avoided prison time
OL,8,Fafter two decades of sexual and
OL,9,Fphysical abuse.
OL,11,FNinety-three-year-old Malcom Phillips
OL,12,Fof Birmingham and his 67-year-old
OL,13,Fassistant Linda Brunning of Sowerby
OL,14,FBridge were found guilty of a string
OL,15,Fof attacks on children aged between
OL,16,Fsix and 15 at Skircoat Lodge at a
OL,17,Ftrial in February.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
