FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1780938366
OL,3,CFormer care home manager avoids jail
OL,4,Cover sexual abuse at children's home
OL,6,FPhillips abused four girls and two
OL,7,Fboys at the home in Halifax between
OL,8,F1976 and 1994 but was deemed unfit to
OL,9,Fstand trial due to "various medical
OL,10,Fconditions" and watched proceedings on
OL,11,Fvideo link from his Birmingham home.
OL,13,FLabelling him a "master manipulator",
OL,14,FJudge Kirstie Watson said he
OL,15,Fcultivated a culture of fear among
OL,16,Fyoung and extremely vulnerable
OL,17,Fchildren.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1780938366
OL,3,CFormer care home manager avoids jail
OL,4,Cover sexual abuse at children's home
OL,6,FBradford Crown Court heard the judge
OL,7,Fsay her only option was to give
OL,8,FPhillips an absolute discharge,
OL,9,Fmeaning no jail time. He was handed a
OL,10,Fsexual harm prevention order.
OL,12,FJudge Watson said: "You were a master
OL,13,Fmanipulator who presented different
OL,14,Ffaces to different people."
OL,16,FBrunning was found guilty of indecent
OL,17,Fassault against one boy and helping
OL,18,FMalcolm Phillips abuse another boy in
OL,19,Fthe 1980s and 1990s. Today, she was
OL,20,Fsentenced to 25 years.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
