FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1780938366
OL,3,CFormer care home manager avoids jail
OL,4,Cover sexual abuse at children's home
OL,6,FSet up in the 1970s as a residential
OL,7,Ftemporary home for children who were
OL,8,Fthe subject of care orders, Bradford
OL,9,FCrown Court heard the home was run by
OL,10,FPhillips "like a prison" where abuse
OL,11,Fwent "unfettered and unreported".
OL,13,FThe court heard children as young as
OL,14,Fnine were targeted for sexual abuse,
OL,15,Fdenied food and threatened that visits
OL,16,Ffrom family would be taken away.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
