FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1780938366
OL,3,CFormer care home manager avoids jail
OL,4,Cover sexual abuse at children's home
OL,6,FSkircoat Lodge closed in 1995 as
OL,7,Fpolice began Operation Screen, an
OL,8,Finvestigation which saw Malcolm
OL,9,FPhillips jailed for seven years for
OL,10,Fsexual offences including rape and
OL,11,Findecent assault.
OL,13,FProtests outside Calderdale Council -
OL,14,Fthe authority responsible for Skircoat
OL,15,FLodge - called for the case to be
OL,16,Freinvestigated.
OL,18,FCalderdale Council has been approached
OL,19,Ffor comment.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
