FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1780938366
OL,3,CFormer care home manager avoids jail
OL,4,Cover sexual abuse at children's home
OL,6,FOperation Henway eventually began in
OL,7,F2017 after more victims campaigned for
OL,8,Ftheir cases to be heard and ultimately
OL,9,Fled to today's sentencing and justice
OL,10,Ffor some of those who suffered at the
OL,11,Fhands of Phillips and Brunning.
OL,13,FToday the court heard a number of
OL,14,Fvictim impact statements from those
OL,15,Fwho have waived their right to
OL,16,Fanonymity.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
