FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1780938366
OL,3,CFormer care home manager avoids jail
OL,4,Cover sexual abuse at children's home
OL,6,FKelly Lees arrived at Skircoat Lodge
OL,7,Fin 1992 as an 11-year-old. The court
OL,8,Fheard how she was punched in the face
OL,9,Fby Brunning and sexually abused by
OL,10,FPhillips.
OL,12,FOn Phillips, she said: "What I
OL,13,Fstruggle to believe is that my abuser,
OL,14,Fwho lives the life of a free man, will
OL,15,Fnever face any consequences of his
OL,16,Factions.
OL,18,F"He should've been in court and this
OL,19,Fshould have been my time to stand up
OL,20,Fto him. I feel he has played the
OL,21,Fsystem and is laughing at me."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1780938366
OL,3,CFormer care home manager avoids jail
OL,4,Cover sexual abuse at children's home
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News prior to today's
OL,7,Fsentencing, Lees said: "They called it
OL,8,Fa children's home. It was a chamber.
OL,9,FThere were children being abused there
OL,10,Fon a daily basis."
OL,12,FKaren Bentham told the court it has
OL,13,Fbeen 13,116 days between her going to
OL,14,FSkircoat Lodge and the conviction of
OL,15,FPhillips.
OL,17,FShe wore a t-shirt in court bearing
OL,18,Fthe names of those she says have died
OL,19,For taken their own lives following
OL,20,Ftheir time at Skircoat Lodge.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
