PN,36109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1780938366
OL,3,CFormer care home manager avoids jail
OL,4,Cover sexual abuse at children's home
OL,6,FAnother victim Angela Radford told the
OL,7,Fcourt that she kept going because "she
OL,8,Fhad to think that one day she would be
OL,9,Fbelieved".
OL,11,FWhile another, Kaz Gray, told ITV News
OL,12,Fafter the sentencing: "Thank you to
OL,13,Fall that supported the survivors over
OL,14,Fthe years."
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/9
